  "slug": "customoregen",
  "title": "CustomOreGen",
  "description": "Adds random blocks to the cobblestone generator to make it more interesting",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://ci.spaceio.xyz/job/CustomOreGen/\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/jenkins/build?jobUrl=https://ci.spaceio.xyz/job/CustomOreGen/\" alt=\"Build Status\">\n  </a>  \n  <br>\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DZwyMaI.png\" alt=\"CustomOreGen Logo\">\n  <br><br>\n\n\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SlnNAZz.gif\" alt=\"Showcase 1, live action of a cobblestone generator generating various blocks\"> \n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Wm0INtG.gif\" alt=\"Showcase 2, showing an example config.yml\">\n  <br><br>\n\n  <a href=\"https://docs.spaceio.xyz/plugin/customoregen/\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/L0m57Bf.png\" alt=\"Documentation page of the plugin\">\n  </a>  \n  <a href=\"https://discord.spaceio.xyz\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vOVCbFe.png\" alt=\"Discord link to join the discord server and get support\">\n  </a>\n  <br><br>\n  <p>\n  CustomOreGen lets you fully customize your SkyBlock server’s cobblestone generator by defining custom materials and spawn probabilities. You can create multiple generator tiers that unlock through permissions or island levels, allowing players to progress as they grow.</p>\n  <h2>Features</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Multiple generator presets based on permissions or island levels</li>\n  <li>Compatible with most SkyBlock plugins</li>\n  <li>Adjustable spawn rates for any block</li>\n  <li>Supports item sub-IDs (legacy versions)</li>\n  <li>Open source and easy to configure</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Compatible plugins</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://download.bentobox.world/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">BentoBox</a> (by Poslovitch and Tastybento)\n    <ul><li>The BentoBox Level Addon is required in order to run CustomOreGen</li></ul>\n  </li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/plugin/iridiumskyblock/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IridiumSkyblock</a> (by IridiumDevelopment)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/askyblock.1220/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ASkyBlock</a> (by Tastybento)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/acidisland.581/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">AcidIsland</a> (by Tastybento)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/uskyblock.2280/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">uSkyBlock</a> (by R4zorax)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/island-world-skyblock-replacement.2757/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Island World</a> (by Gnacik)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/%E2%9A%A1%EF%B8%8F-superiorskyblock2-%E2%9A%A1%EF%B8%8F-the-best-core-on-market-%E2%9A%A1%EF%B8%8F-1-16-support.63905/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SuperiorSkyblock2</a> (by Oma_R)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/plotsquared-v4-v5-out-now.1177/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">PlotSquared</a> (by IntellectualSites)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/Songoda/fabledskyblock\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">FabledSkyBlock</a> (by Songoda)</li>\n</ul>\n\n</p>\n\n",
